## Another check for proportional odds assumption ##

sf <- function(y){
  c('Y>=1' = qlogis(mean(y >= 1)),
    'Y>=2' = qlogis(mean(y >= 2)),
    'Y>=3' = qlogis(mean(y >= 3)),
    'Y>=4' = qlogis(mean(y >= 4)),
    'Y>=5' = qlogis(mean(y >= 5)))
    }

(s1 <- with(astra, summary(as.numeric(willingness) ~ vax_scaled + age_scaled*frame, fun=sf)))
